title: 'Private' Justin Bieber will sue you if you don't take down his nude pic
text: 'Private' Justin Bieber will sue you if you don't take down his nude pic Tuesday, 13 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) *Washington, Oct. 9(ANI): After Justin Bieber 's nude pictures took over the internet, the singer's legal team is now sending out notices to get them down.* Washington, Oct. 9(ANI): After Justin Bieber's nude pictures took over the internet, the singer's legal team is now sending out notices to get them down. According to a source, the 21-year-old singer has claimed that his privacy was invaded by this act and has asked every media outlet, who published his picture that was shot in Bora Bora, to take it down immediately, reports TMZ.com. The picture that was taken without the 'Baby' hit-maker's knowledge shows him naked right before jumping into the pool. (ANI)
